originalText.text: Rowena does a fantastic job! I had my first Deep Pore Cleansing Facial with her a few months ago and she was very kind and focused. She had good recommendations for keeping my skin clear and recommended drinking a lot of water before my next facial, which is great advice to make the facial better/less painful! I will be continuing to see Rowena for the facials. Definitely recommend!
